These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, old-henry, cain, vegafina, ritmeester
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, drama, western, mystery, romance
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, hot-chocolate, milk
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person drinking milk is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking coffee##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Cigar         | old-henry  | tiparillo    | vegafina | cain    | ritmeester  |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | horror | western | mystery | romance  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Beverage         | mirinda | hot-chocolate    | iced-tea | coffee  | milk |

