.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, september, july, august, november
There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, yellow, turquise, lilac, green
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, cricket, surfing, sailing
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the russian is the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who likes yellow##1
13. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Birthday          | july        | november | september     | august      | april  |
| Color           | yellow   | turquise | green    | lilac | azure |
| Sport   | cricket | surfing     | sailing | soccer    | lacrosse  |
| Nationality   | russian     | indonesian | argentine    | spanish      | mexican    |

