.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different games are played: poker, backgammon, domino, go, scrabble
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, traveling, writing
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer, skiing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, rock, classical, folk, disco
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 9. the fan of disco is in the middle##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing poker##1
13. the person playing go is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Game      | go          | domino  | backgammon       | poker     | scrabble      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | traveling  | reading   | cooking    |
| Sport   | sailing        | skiing | parkour | soccer    | snowboarding   |
| Music-Genre     | country   | classical | disco      | rock | folk |

