There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blood-red, yellow, chestnut, coral
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, cola, milk, lemonade
 1. the person who's hobby is soy-milkd-games is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's hobby is soy-milkd-games##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating zucchini is the person who likes yellow##1
11. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
