The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, funk, indie, rock
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, bike, car, roller, train
 1. the fan of d&b is the person driving the car##1
 2. the person driving the car is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the fan of country is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
10. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
11. the person playing snooker is on the right of the fan of funk##1
12. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Game          | bridge    | snooker  | whist | scrabble    | domino      |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery | martial-arts | drama  | satire | time-travel |
| Music-Genre   | funk           | d&b      | rock      | indie        | country     |
| Transport         | bike         | car  | taxi   | roller       | train  |

