 1. the person traveling to paris is the italian##1
 2. the chinese is the person eating pomegranate##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the german is the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the mexican##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person eating lime is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the mexican##1
 9. the german is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating eggplant##1
11. the mexican is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
12. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the german##1
13. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
