.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-16::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk, sprite
5 different games are played: domino, poker, chess, backgammon, mah-jongg
5 different pets are kept: hamster, fish, mouse, dog, guinea-pig
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, prince, havana, bluemaster, cain
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 2. the person playing domino is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person playing chess is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
 9. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
10. the person drinking cola is the prince-smoker##1
11. the person playing backgammon is the cain-smoker##1
12. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |       3       |     4      |    5     |
| Beverage      | sprite        | cola       | hot-chocolate | soy-milk   | juice    |
| Game   | backgammon           | domino     | chess        | poker      | mah-jongg   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig     | fish  | mouse         | hamster | dog   |
| Cigar         | cain | prince | bongani      | havana | bluemaster |

