 1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of country##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the russian##1
 6. the chinese is on the right of the indonesian##1
