 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the russian is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the french is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
12. the person who likes lavender is the fan of house##1
