 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the person traveling to prague is the person who likes chestnut##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is the townhouse house##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person traveling to miami is the cape-cod house##1
 8. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
12. the person traveling to paris is in the middle##1
13. the victorian house is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the cottage house is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1

